FBIS3-28154 "dreas023__a94010" FBIS-EAS-94-023-A Document Type:Daily Report 3 February 1994 ANNEX Mongolia Democratic Union Issues Statement on Corruption OW0202223194 Ulaanbaatar MONTSAME in English 1944 GMT 2 Feb 94 -- FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY OW0202223194 Ulaanbaatar MONTSAME Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Ulaanbaatar, February 2 (OANA-MONTSAME) -- The Presidium of the Mongolian Democratic Union made a statement, addressing its members and supporters. In the statement it is noted that abuse of power and bribery are widely spreading in the country among a state and government high officials, reaching the level capable to cause a threat to the national security. In this connection the Mongolian Democratic Union announces about its intention to liven up its political activity.
